                     </persName>
                     
                  , did make an assault, putting him in coporal fear and danger of his life, and stealing from his person a silver watch, value 20 s. a base metal watch-key, value 1 d. and a pair of silver shoe-buckles, value 8 s. the property of the said 
                     <persName id="t17800405-8-person118">
                        John
                         Monteith
                     <interp inst="t17800405-8-person118" type="surname" value="Monteith"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t17800405-8-person118" type="given" value="John"></interp>
