             sworn.</p>
               <p>I have known Graham ever since he has been in the regiment. I never heard any thing against him before this; he has bore a very good character.</p>
               <p>ALL THREE <rs id="t17800405-8-verdict39" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17800405-8-verdict39" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               NOT GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the First Middlesex Jury before Mr. Justice Nares.</p>
